Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-ducklake
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-ducklake
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, postgresql-PGVERSION
Description: DuckLake lakehouse extension for PostgreSQL PGVERSION
 pg_ducklake manages DuckLake tables inside PostgreSQL, backed by DuckDB
 execution and Parquet files. It requires shared_preload_libraries =
 'pg_ducklake' before CREATE EXTENSION.
